title: The Passing Bells S01E02 - GHOST DOG
description:
The Passing Bells will see the conflict of the First World War unfold through the eyes of two young men. Paddy Gibson and Jack Lowden play the lead roles of Thomas and Michael, two men for whom the war has no mercy. The story follows them over five years, as they grow older, lose comrades and find love amidst the horrors of the war.

Episode 2 of 5:

World War I drama. 1915. On the eastern front, Michael is forced to make a terrible choice, while on the western front Tommy's regiment experiments with a dangerous new weapon.
